<br>
Now take the real worl. We are all humans, all have the same basic needs and desires. Yet, we are unable to understand each other very well at all if the slightest difference is present. Religion, race, age, economic status, nationality, life outlook, marital status, language, etc are things that can make us totally unable to understand the other's point of view.<br>
<br>
So in the world of make believe that is Norrath, we have not only each of the above mentioned things, but also the added difference of being different sentient life forms. <br>
<br>
Since this is not Star Trek(c) (do not want to get sued) all races do not get along, all races do not like or understand each other. Some races are completly dedicated to wiping the other one out.<br>
<br>
So given this set of circumstances, how the heck can anyone have the audacity, the sheer unmitigated hubris to pretend thye understand what THE correct for of RP is.<br>
<br>
In my opinion, the best RPers are the ones that get beyond the kindergarten Aulde Englishe speak and the easy alignment/race RP and develop a unique way of life and play it. The more I have to work to try and figure out if it is the perosnaility of the person behind the toon; or a complex character that the person is playing out the more impresed I am. Life is complicated, too complicated to reduce to a series of dos and don'ts. Be creative, be unique.<br>
<br>
Also, this is still the RP Preferred server not he RP required server.  Some of us came here because of the other unique aspects of this server. I like RP and try to always remember that many people came here only because of the RP situation, but I RP Police also have to understand that this is only ONE of the unique elements of our server. <br>
<br>
Borm SteelWarrior of the 28th Season <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ugozaro.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gozaro</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.trafficblast.com/lott/data/gozaro_head.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 34<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/14/01 2:16:42 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=171.topic&index=6>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.trafficblast.com/im/data/gozar_head.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_sad.gif" align=absmiddle>  You know what I'd like to see =)</span><hr size=1> I'd like to see a EQ RP guide.   maybe someone can direct me to one that exists.<br>
